FBIS3-38917 "drweu027_p_94005" FBIS-WEU-94-027 Document Type:Daily Report 9 Feb 1994 GREECE Labor Confederation Opposes War Operations in Bosnia NC0802195594 Athens Elliniki Radhiofonia Radio Network in Greek 1800 GMT 8 Feb 94 NC0802195594 Athens Elliniki Radhiofonia Radio Network Language: Greek Article Type:BFN [Text] YSEE [Greek General Confederation of Labor] issued a statement today condemning any war operations in the war zone of Bosnia and opposes our country's involvement. It also points out that the massacre of civilians in Sarajevo, which it condemns unequivocally, cannot be an alibi for a military intervention.
